ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of GORDON MacINNIS of Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of three years, in the place of Susan LeBlanc Robichaud.
